{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO849474B0481P0D1N001340", "chronotag": "1742567157257", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CS1340", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1340", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CSVIEECO", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO419610B0481P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0481", "triAmendement": "abaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaejs", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "Gouvernement", "gouvernementRef": "PO855052", "acteurRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "groupePolitiqueRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "le Gouvernement"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article PREMIER", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. PREMIER", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE PREMIER", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0481.asp#D_Article_1er"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": "Apres", "numero": "8", "alineaDesignation": "Apr\u00e8s l'alin\u00e9a 8"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": "Sous r\u00e9serve de son traitement par les services de l'Assembl\u00e9e nationale et de sa recevabilit\u00e9", "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apr&#x00E8;s l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;8, ins&#x00E9;rer l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a suivant&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;VIII&nbsp;<i>bis</i>&nbsp;<i>(nouveau).</i>&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;L&#x2019;article L.&nbsp;4261&#x2011;1 du code de la d&#x00E9;fense est abrog&#x00E9;.&nbsp;&#x00BB;</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement vise &#x00E0; supprimer le Conseil sup&#x00E9;rieur de la r&#x00E9;serve militaire.</p><p>Dans un souci de limitation des redondances, le r&#x00F4;le de consultation et de r&#x00E9;flexion exerc&#x00E9; par le CSRM pourrait &#x00EA;tre efficacement repris par d&#x2019;autres structures d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; existantes, telles que la D&#x00E9;l&#x00E9;gation Interarm&#x00E9;es aux R&#x00E9;serves (DIAR), qui assure la coordination des r&#x00E9;serves au sein des diff&#x00E9;rentes arm&#x00E9;es et services.</p><p>Cet amendement d&#x00E9;coule de la m&#x00E9;thode du Gouvernement, fond&#x00E9;e sur trois crit&#x00E8;res :</p><p>&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Premier crit&#x00E8;re : la redondance avec d&#x2019;autres services ou organismes.</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Deuxi&#x00E8;me crit&#x00E8;re : l&#x2019;activit&#x00E9; r&#x00E9;elle de la commission.</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Troisi&#x00E8;me crit&#x00E8;re : l&#x2019;impact de la suppression sur la lisibilit&#x00E9; de l&#x2019;action publique.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-03-21", "datePublication": "2025-03-21", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "ET", "libelle": "En traitement"}, "sousEtat": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO849474B0481P0D1N001340?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "c d\u00e9fense", "divisionCodeLoi": "L4261-1"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}